            <h1 class="page-header">Organization Structure
                <small>It's Nice to Meet You!</small>
            </h1>
            <p>The GVF functions through a structure at the following levels.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Advisory Council</li>
                <li>Board of Trustees</li>
                <li>Governing Body</li>
                <li>Fellows</li>
                <li>Researches</li>
            </ul>

            <br>

            <div class="row">
